Version 0.7
- Fixed #includes and #ifdefs for recent kernels/distribs/compilers.
- FreeBSD support (Bert Driehuis)
- Major speed improvement for serial receivers with the kernel module
  (Thanks to Stewart Scott for helping debug this).
- Integrated latest modifications for WR2000 series:
  SetMode in AM
- Special handling of 2.55GHz-2.65GHz ?
- More interpolation in SetFrequency
- Features missing:
  RMD_6k, RMD_2500 in SetMode2000()
  LastVco* in SetFreq2000
  New 5769 chip ?
  SetAgc2000, SetIfg2000, GetSLevel2000 not updated yet
- Major changes in SetBfo2000
- AGC supported 
 
Version 0.6

- Source tree reorganized

Version 0.4

- Kernel module for all receivers, internal/external

Version 0.3

- Serial receiver support (not as module)
- RPM binary distribution
- Kernel module ("make module") (NOT YET)
- wrlib subdirectory with new WiNRADiO source code
- Port autodetect
- Demo scripts

Version 0.2

- Asynchronous spectrum scan
- Stations database
- Support for external receivers (not tested)
- Auto scan resolution
- IFShift (not tested)
- Manual pages
- Keyboard shortcuts
- "configure" script
- "make install", "make uninstall"
- CVS Source code management
